import React, { useContext, useEffect, useState } from 'react' // import context from './usecontext' import { useLocation, useSearchParams } from 'react-router-dom' const Deliveryaddress = () => { const[name,setname]=useState() const[email,setemail]=useState() const[mobile,setmobile]=useState() const[address,setaddress]=useState() const[cash,setcash]=useState() const[idd,setidd]=useState() const[date,setdate]=useState() const[expectday,setexpectday]=useState() const location = useLocation(); const [params]=useSearchParams() const id=params.get("id") useEffect(()=>{ show() mycomponent() },[]) const show=async()=>{ try{ const res= await fetch(`http://localhost:9000/api/useraddress/${id}`,{ method:"get" }) if(res.ok){ const result= await res.json() if(result.statuscode===1){ setname(result.data.name) setemail(result.data.email) setmobile(result.data.mobile) setaddress(result.data.address) setcash(result.data.cash) setidd(result.data._id) } } }catch(err){ alert(err) } } const mycomponent = () => { const currentdate = new Date(); const year = currentdate.getFullYear(); const month = currentdate.getMonth() + 1; // add 1 to get correct month const day = currentdate.getDate(); // get day of the month const expectedday=day+4; // const formattedDate = `${day}/${month}/${year}`; const formattedDate=day+"/"+month+"/"+year // const newdate1=`${expectedday}/${month}/${year}`; const newdate1=expectedday+"/"+month+"/"+year setdate(formattedDate); setexpectday(newdate1) } return (
